Dealer  -
Dealer
Responsibilities
Overall responsible for quality of dealing serviceMaintain high dealing standards and keep dealing errors to the minimum.Ensure that dealing principles, company policies, regulatory requirements are adhered to.Provide technical views on customers’ investment strategiesExecute trades for equities, including order taking from clientsServe retail clientsWork with back office to resolve client issues.Handle trade disputes cases promptly and ensure outcomes are fair to both customer and company.Ensure customer complaints are handled according to SOP.Manage process changes in the dealing room to enhance efficiency and effectiveness of daily work.Conduct regular training/briefing sessions to improve the working knowledge of staff in the dealing room Requirements: Degree, diploma or professional qualification with Broker-Dealer Representative licenceHaving at least 5 years working experience as Retail Dealer in the Securities IndustryGood command in English both verbal and writtenHave good communication and interpersonal skillsProactive and self-initiative orientedAble to work under pressure and tight deadlineTeam player with ability to work under pressure and drive to succeed in our ever changing environment Interested applicants should write in with a detailed resume stating qualifications, experience, present and expected salary and a non-returnable photograph to:Human ResourcesPT. DBS VICKERS SECURITIES INDONESIADBS Bank TowerCiputra World 1,32/FJl. Prof.Dr.Satrio  Kav. 3-5Jakarta 12940Orhr_recruit@id.dbsvickers.com(Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)
